WEBVTT

00:07:57.759 --> 00:08:00.207
Flags were used as identity weapons.

00:08:00.969 --> 00:08:05.240
And now, in 2019, the Nazi flag
is banned from being flown

00:08:05.264 --> 00:08:06.943
by anyone in Germany

00:08:06.967 --> 00:08:10.279
and anyone in Austria, in Hungary,
in Russia and in Ukraine.

00:08:11.010 --> 00:08:12.187
Think about that.

00:08:12.211 --> 00:08:14.334
It's a piece of cloth, but it's banned.

00:08:15.031 --> 00:08:16.925
On its face, that sounds crazy.

00:08:17.846 --> 00:08:20.469
But I don't think anyone
in this room would disagree

00:08:20.493 --> 00:08:21.922
that it's probably good.

00:08:22.796 --> 00:08:24.480
Sounds a lot like a weapon.

00:08:26.383 --> 00:08:27.839
As a vexillologist,

00:08:27.863 --> 00:08:30.544
sometimes the most interesting
thing about a flag